the war on kids is a 2011 american documentary film directed by robert &lt;unk&gt; and produced by robert &lt;unk&gt; . the film is based on the short story of the same name by robert &lt;unk&gt; . the film was nominated for an academy award for best documentary feature . the film was selected as the american entry for the best foreign language film at the 84th academy awards , but was not nominated .